            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: Shen KR, Meyers BF, Larner JM, Jones DR, American College of Chest Physicians. Special treatment issues in lung cancer: ACCP evidence-based clinical practice guidelines (2nd edition). Chest. 2007 Sep;132(3 Suppl):290S-305S.</p></div></p>
